<!DOCTYPE HTML>

<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <title>letter page</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" charset="UTF-8"/>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

{{> layout/navigation}}

<div class="my-5"></div>

<div class="container col-lg-6 col-md-9 justify-content-center" id="read-letter-space">
  <div class="row ">
    <div id="letter-img"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <h1 id="letter-title"></h1>
  </div>
  <hr class="mb-1">
  <div class="row" id="letter-info-space">
    <div class="d-flex">
      <div class="d-inline-flex" id="letter-post-date"></div>
      <div class="flex-fill"></div>
      <div class="d-inline-flex">
        <p class="" id="author-name"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="letter-content"></div>
  <div id="login-page-div" style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 500px; display: none">
    <hr>
    <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
      <h3 class="text-primary">
        이 편지를 더 읽고 싶다면
      </h3>
      <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">
        회원가입/로그인이 필요해요!
      </h3>
      <h5>로그인도 회원가입도 30초만에!</h5>
      <h5>간편하게 로그인하고 무료로 읽어보세요!</h5>
      <button class="btn btn-primary mt-2" id="go-to-login-page-btn" style="width: 150px">
        회원가입/로그인
      </button>
    </div>
    <hr>
  </div>
</div>

<script
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="/js/letter/read/letterRead.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
